extends layout

block content
    
    div.container
        h1 Resume Builder
        p.lead
            | This experiment is to create a single resume blurb. Insert the information for a job and it will be presented, in what is hopefully a pleasing manner, to you. Some of the details will be present only upon clicking.

        form.container(role='form')
            div.form-group
                div.col-sm-8
                    label(for='company-name') Company Name
                    input#company-name.form-control(type='text')
                    p.help-block What was the name of the company that you worked for?

                div.col-sm-4
                    label(for='company-link') Company Link (Optional) 
                    input#company-link.form-control(type='url')

            div.form-group.col-sm-12
                label(for='company-location') Company Location (Optional)
                input#company-location.form-control(type='text')

            div.form-group.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
                label(for='start-date') Start Date
                input#start-date.form-control(type='date')

            div.form-group.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
                label(for='end-date') End Date
                input#end-date.form-control(type='date')
                
                div.checkbox
                    label 
                        input(type='checkbox') 
                        | Currently working here
                
            div.form-group.col-sm-12
                label(for='description') Description (Optional)
                // Sounds good... 
                textarea.form-control(rows=8) 
